canvases.label: Untitled--Very good! I think we fit in beautifully with the environment. The life we live comes naturally to us. We are aristocratic, well-bred: a cultured and civilized couple. I have never had to work a day in my life. We have always been affluent. I don't care if people like the way we live--All we want is peace and quiet. Lewis Callaghan June 16th. 1982, from the series Rich and Poor
